About the HEPA Certification

About the HEPA Certification

Simply put, the HEPA designation applies to any device capable of filtering, in a single pass, at least 99.97% of particles with a diameter of 0.3 Âµm or larger. Particles in the 0.3 Âµm range are the most difficult to filter. Johnny Vac is proud to offer a wide range of HEPA certified bags, filters and devices.

FOR USE IN SANI-AIR ELECTRIC AIR FRESHENER - Open can by pulling ring tab off.  Fold a wick and place the two free ends down in opening of can making sure one end touches bottom.  The exposed portion should be formed into a loop.  Adjust the loop larger for more fragrance, smaller for less fragrance.  Carefully place can into air freshener.

FOR USE IN SANI-AIR BATTERY AIR FRESHENER - Same as directions for Sani-Air Electric Air Freshener.  For optimum performance use two or three wicks.

FOR USE IN SANI-AIR STILL AIR FRESHENER - Open can by pulling ring tab off.  Fold an All Purpose Wick accordion style along perforations.  Place one end down in opening of can making sure the wick touches bottom.  The esposed portion should be fanned out fully for optimum evaporation.  Carefully place can into air freshener.  In case of too much evaporation simply cut down height of wick.

The ProForce uprights provide exceptional cleaning in a high-filtration upright to improve reach, durability, and soil removal. This top-of-the-line commercial HEPA vacuum comes with excellent onboard tools. The powerful ProForce contains a high-performance dual-motor system and a low profile, L-shaped head perfectly for vacuuming under and around furniture.

Features

  • Powerful Suction - The high-performance dual motor system maintains power to both the brush roll and the suction motor.
  • Long 50 Foot Cord - The extra-long 50-foot power cord allows you to clean large areas without plugging and re-plugging.

ProductDescriptionEN:
Rolly is a brand new ultra-compact scrubber dryer made by Ghibli & Wirbel. It is a result of experience of our engineers and product experts. Rolly is the right answer to the professional cleaning demand. A unique mix of distinctive solutions - compact dimensions, a special unlockable handle and combined brush head/squeegee system (both patented) and the last generation lithium batteries- makes Rolly the ideal solution for small or crowded cleaning areas.

Rolly Scrubber Dryer - Technical video from ghibli&wirbel on Vimeo.

YOU CAN GO AND WORK WHEREVER YOU WANT

Compact and reactive, Rolly perfectly works in every environment.it's dimensions, combined with the new handle with unlocking system, guarantee the best cleaning results, even in congested areas and in narrow spaces. The swivel wheels assure the max manoeuvrability.

USER FRIENDLY

Intuitive control panel. Machine easy to set upâ¦ everything always under control. âColouredâ parts - yellow (or blue, depending on the model), levers, knobs, ...clearly indicate where the user can âput the handsâ preparing the machine for work or while using it.

EASY TO FILL AND DRAIN

Solution tank: easy to transport and fill (under sink, tap). Practical cover with percentage graduation for chemical dosage. Recovery tank: foldable and removable, thanks to its click-clack system it perfectly seals the recovery tank, so avoiding any water leaking effect either in transport or while working. The tank can be easily transported and drained like a bucket.

EFFORTLESS MAINTENANCE

Immediate brush click on/off system (by button). Sliding brush deck. Squeegee blades simple to install/remove.

ROLLY HOSTS IN A COMPLETE COMFORT. THE LITHIUM BATTERIES: THE POWER IN A CASE

Nothing to extract, remove, prepare for the batteries location. They stay inside a practical case which can be promptly inserted in the back of the machine.

EASY TO TRANSPORT, PARK, STORE

Rolly is really small and above all light (only 23 kg). When it is not in action it can be moved, parked or stored everywhere without any effort

MANY ACCESORIES, TO MATCH EVERY SPECIAL NEED

The standard equipment of all the Rolly variants is really rich. In addition there is a wide range of accessories (batteries, charger, brushes, â¦) to wear Rolly in the best way in every situation.

The wireless vacuum cleaner JV259CH (X30) combines performance and elegance with a sleek, modern design. Weighing just 9.25 lbs (4,2 kg), itâs easy to carry the vacuum from room to room and even into hard-to-reach areas.

Automatic Self Cleaning System
and Dirt Detection

With its smooth and stylish charging dock, the cordless vacuum cleaner JV259CH is easy to recharge. Simply connect the vacuum to the dock and press a button, and you're all set: in addition to charging, it empties automatically, with the dust being collected in a separate compartment from the vacuum itself!

And by simply changing the brush, you can transform your stick vacuum into an unbeatable tool for cleaning short and long pile carpets, sofas, mattresses and even your car interior.

The vacuum is also equipped with indicator lights on the front, allowing you to see under sofas and other dark places.

https://youtu.be/wiPZ_E9tujg

Personalization for Customers

The PUDU Open Platform allows users to customize KETTYPROâs expressions, voice, and content, enabling easy operation and truly differentiated services.

Multiple tables can be served in a single run thanks to precise positioning and optimal path planning. Achieve more with less! KettyBot Pro can cruise within designated areas to offer customers free snacks and drinks while simultaneously broadcasting services and promotions.

It offers two configurations thanks to its removable trays and optional rear cover. This versatility allows the robot to be adapted to your needs: full delivery mode or streamlined reception/marketing mode, delivering an all-in-one solution for your establishment.

Automatic Navigation Planning

Laser & visual dual navigation solution helps to detect obstacles more accurately, making the robot safer. It can easily maneuver through very tight spaces.

Multi-robot Cooperation for Higher Efficiency. Powered by PUDU Scheduler, KettyBot Pro can directly communicate with any robot in the same network.

ProductTitleFR: Ensemble d'installation Doc It - blanc
ProductTitleEN: Doc It Installation Kit - White
ProductDescriptionFR:
AUCUNE TRADUCTION FRANÃAISE

* Hose management system installation kit required (KIT7500RK)

The Canavac Doc-IT is It"...an easy solution to central vacuum hose management. Over the years the number one complaint of central vacuum owners is "Where do I store that bulky hose?" Doc-IT is the answer. A hose storage device is located in your walls with a small door allowing you access to the hose handle. The Doc-IT is fully electric allowing you to powerfully clean up to 3000 square feet of living space with a single hose and then store it away effortlessly with a simple touch. For larger homes add an additional Doc-IT or two. The Doc-iT is the only retractable hose system that allows you to connect a 120 volt electric powerhead right at the hose handle. With Doc-IT there is no need for an extension cord to run your powerhead.

A motor is activated by fingertip controls on the handle grip allowing you to release the hose retract the hose and turn your central vacuum system on from the handle.

The location for the installation should be where the maximum coverage in the home is possible typically near the center of the house. This can be achieved by using a 50' measuring tape or pre-measured 50' cord for 45' hose. Use a 60' measuring tape or a pre-measured 60' cord for a 55' hose.

This Finish Kit is the first step in the Doc IT Kit Builder and includes the following:

  • Retractor Cabinet Assembly
  • Storage Wall Cavity Liners
    • (1) 3-3/8" x 30"
    • (2) 3-3/8" x 44"
    • (2) 33" x 44"
  • Fitting Adapter Hose to PVC
  • (4) Drywall Screws
  • (2) Insulated Male Faston Connectors for Low Voltage Connectors
  • Rough-In Kit Manual
  • Cardboard Protective Cover - DO NOT DISCARD

The Doc-IT is an easy installation in new construction but it is also possible to retrofit a Doc-It in your existing home.

Hose Storage Cavity (inside wall): 30 1/2" wide x 41 3/4" high x 3 1/2 " deep

It uses high-flow negative-pressure ventilation and an efficient filter to trap particles in the debris bin, effectively preventing secondary pollution.

The PUDU MT1 is equipped with AI-powered cameras capable of recognizing and identifying different types of waste in real time. It continuously learns and improves through deep learning and database updates.

SEE THE BROCHURE USER GUIDE Its modular design also allows for easy maintenance. The dust bins, brushes, and other consumables can be removed within minutes, making replacement simple and extending the machineâs overall lifespan.
